            "title": "港股開市︱重越二萬五 恒指升96點報25095點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段略為反彈，恒生指數甫開市即收復二萬五關口，報25095點，升96點或0.39%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5689點，升45點或0.8%；國企指數以8958點開市，升41點或0.46%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股今早升多跌少，今日收市後派成績表的阿里巴巴(09988)開報116.8元，升0.86%；騰訊(00700)開報595.5元，升0.25%；美團(03690)開報102.4元，升0.68%；小米(01810)開報52.9元，跌0.38%。滙控(00005)開報100.3元，跌0.3%；友邦(01299)開報72.75元，升0.35%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">剛公布配股集資的股份，今早則個別發展。晶泰控股(02228)開報9.95元，跌1.09%；和鉑醫藥(02142)開報13.18元，升3.78%；科笛(02487)開報9.3元，跌2.62%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15214363-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%94-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8796%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125095%e9%bb%9e",
